chmod 644  file name - give permission for user read , write and exicute
chmod -R 655 directory - to change the current directory for subdirectories
chmod 777  directoryname - to give a full permission for group user other
chown [OPTIONS] user:group file/directory
chown john:users myfile.txt
chown alice:staff mydirectory
chown -R john:users mydirectory
chgrp balu nikhil - to change balu group to  nikhil permission. (to cahnge the permission groups only used this command)	
